        <h2>Troubleshooting Common Problems</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Bot isn't visiting:</strong> Make sure you use TCP tunneling and NOT HTTP tunneling to avoid the confirmation page</li>
            <li><strong>Localhost not connected:</strong> Check the port again, make sure your local server port is the one being tunneled by Pinggy</li>
        </ul>
